{"per_page":10,"total":5,"current":2,"data":[{"title":"CocosCreator 编辑器入门","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>CocosCreator是一个完整的游戏开发解决方案，包括了 cocos2d-x 引擎的 JavaScript 实现，以及能更快速开发游戏所需要的各种图形界面工具。在 Cocos2d-x 基础上实现了彻底脚本化、组件化和数据驱动等特点。</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/CocosCreator_Base","categories":["CocosCreator","ComputerScience","Game"]},{"title":"字符编码介绍","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>一个规则,这个规则可以将字符映射到唯一一种状态(二进制字符串)，这就是编码.</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/Encode","categories":["ComputerScience"]},{"title":"Go 笔记","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">package main</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">import &quot;fmt&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">func main() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tfmt.Println(&quot;Hello, 世界&quot;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","link":"2021/06/19/Go_note","categories":["ComputerScience","Go"]},{"title":"色彩笔记","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>在计算机中，计算机本身并不能直接通过名字识别色彩，而是通过数字完成记录的。<br>\n<img src=\"https://image.boxueio.com/color-basics-2@2x.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/Color_Notes","categories":["Fun","UI"]},{"title":"如何使用GitHub","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>最近要给一个新人做一个GitHub的介绍。<br>\n本次介绍内容主要为两点：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>什么是GitHub；</li>\n<li>为什么要用GitHub；</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/HowToUseGithub","categories":["ComputerScience","Git"]},{"title":"iOS-学习基础和文章推荐","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>文档用于更好的规划好自己的 iOS 学习, 准确的定位的目前所处的位置，以及文章的查找。</p>\n<p><code>Objective-C 2.0</code>  <code>Swift 5.0</code></p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/HowToLearniOSBase","categories":["ComputerScience","iOS"]},{"title":"如何更好的自主学习？","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>自主学习是教育的最高境界，而一些方法则可以帮助有效的自主学习</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/Howtotakenotes","categories":["Fun"]},{"title":"Objective-C对象模型","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>在OC中，每一个对象都有一个名为 isa 的指针，指向该对象的类。这个类描述了一系列它的实例相关内容，包括成员变量的列表，成员函数的列表等。每一个对象都可以接受消息，而对象能够接收的消息列表是保存在它所对应的类中。</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/Inside_The_OC_Object_Model","categories":["ComputerScience","iOS"]},{"title":"iOS-剖析UIView","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>UIView在iOS中则是在屏幕上用来管理一块矩形区域的对象，也是iOS开发中最为基础的UI控件。</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/IOS_UIview","categories":["ComputerScience","iOS"]},{"title":"JavaScript 学习总结","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>JavaScript是一种高级的、解释型的编程语言。JavaScript是一门基于原型、函数先行的语言，是一门多范式的语言，它支持面向对象编程，命令式编程，以及函数式编程。<br>\n<code>JavaScript</code>虽然非常灵活，但是制定相对应的编程规范，可以增强代码的阅读性，提高代码的质量，避免因为灵活性而导致代码过于杂乱。</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/JavaScriptSummary","categories":["ComputerScience","JavaScript","Web"]}]}